@Aceron4 wrote:

[quote=“Ashton51, post:5, topic:386759”][quote author=Aceron4 link=topic=482530.msg3533685#msg3533685 date=1300398023]

Bah, Don’t EVER edit any file with a .class extension. Those files are only to be modified by the compiler. Only edit the files with a .java extension…

Doesnt look like hes editing a file with a .class extension. That just looks like an extremely messed up client.java (and yes ive downloaded a source that had something like that before)
[/quote]
Oh, I haven’t actually ever even opened a .class file before, That is one shitty client then. I would recommend getting a new one simply because whoever made that is a complete idiot.[/quote]

Hahaha, yeah I agree with Ashton … you if I was the one coding that source I would throw it in the trash and find a new one. :I
